data.description: HIGHLY DESIRED GATED VIZCAYA! 2 bedroom 2.5 bathroom plus office that can be used as bedroom (no closet). Neutral tile downstairs & gorgeous high quality wood look laminate upstairs. Kitchen offers newer stainless appliances, over sized sink, maple cabinets. Decorator touches throughout include custom crown molding & baseboards. Plenty of room to entertain indoors and outdoors.Cozy living space perfect for relaxing. Master bathroom & half bathroom have been tastefully upgraded. Master bedroom offers a walk in closet with custom built ins. Office upstairs has built in desks & closet can be added to make it a 3rd bedroom. Jack & Jill bathroom. Laundry room upstairs. Private patio with retractable awing surrounded with lush landscape & hedge. Newer water heater & a/c unit. Excellent schools!  For showings call or text: 706-577-3870
